## Data Licensing Notice

This MIT License applies ONLY to the LandScope application source code.
It does NOT apply to the datasets referenced or loaded by the application.

Data from the following providers remains under their respective terms:

- **Texas Geographic Information Office (TxGIO) / TNRIS** — Texas Parcels
- **U.S. Fish & Wildlife Service (USFWS)** — National Wetlands Inventory
- **Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA)** — National Flood Hazard Layer
- **Homeland Infrastructure Foundation-Level Data (HIFLD)** — Electric Transmission Lines

See `docs/DATA_SOURCES.md` for details on each dataset's licence and terms of use.
